details.message: Crossing the border of the states of US-NY and US-NJ.

maneuver.instruction: Turn right onto East Tremont Avenue.

steps.destinations: I 95 South, US 1 South: Cross Bronx Expressway, George Washington Bridge

maneuver.instruction: Turn right to take the I 95 South ramp toward Cross Bronx Expressway/George Washington Bridge.
Keep left to stay on I 95.
Keep left to take I 95/NJTP/New Jersey Turnpike.
Take exit 17 onto NJ 495 East toward Lincoln Tunnel.

steps.destinations: NJ 495 East: Linkoln Tunnel, New York City

maneuver.instruction: Keep left to take NJ 495 East toward Linkoln Tunnel/New York City.
Take the US 1 South/US 9 South exit toward NJ 3.
Keep left to take US 1/US 9/Tonnelle Avenue.
Turn left to take the ramp.
Your destination is on the right.
